commodities.order
Class ContractOrderLine

java.lang.Object
  commodities.order.ContractOrderLine
public class ContractOrderLine
extends Object

The ContractOrderLine contains the information for a complete buy and sell ContractOrder along with any supporting fields that do not directly relate to either the buy or sell order.
